  "StockRole": "Scout",
  "YangsThoughts": "Hellespont Industrials built this for the Capellan Confederation on Sun Tzu Liao's personal commission. Stealth armor, MASC, Vibroblade, the whole package. The HAR-101 uses mixed tech from the Clans while the HAR-111 is a pure Inner Sphere build that they actually exported to the Magistracy and Fronc Reaches. Both versions are built around the same idea, get in faster than anyone expects, do damage, disappear before they can respond. That is a concept that works regardless of what tech you fill it with.",
